# 📁 File Organizer – Automation Script

## 📌 Problem Statement

This project is aimed at developing a Python script that automatically organizes files in a target directory based on file types (e.g., Documents, Images, Videos, Others).

---

## 🗂 Features

- Scans a target directory and classifies files based on extensions.
- Automatically creates category folders (Documents, Images, Videos, Others).
- Moves files into the appropriate folders.
- Includes exception handling for errors.
- Displays a summary o